    SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[ContactNo], [e].[CreationTime], [e].[CreatorUserId], [e].[DateOfBirth], [e].[DeleterUserId], [e].[DeletionTime], [e].[Department], [e].[EmployeeNumber], [e].[HireDate], [e].[IsDeleted], [e].[LastModificationTime], [e].[LastModifierUserId], [e].[ManagerId], [e].[NationalIdNumber], [e].[Position], [e].[UserId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Name]

        SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name]

) AS [s]

    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [e0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [e1] ON [s].[Id] = [e1].[EmployeeId]

        SELECT 1
        FROM [AbpSettings] AS [a]
        WHERE [a].[Name] = @__name_0 AND [a].[TenantId] IS NULL AND [a].[UserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
